---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';

const shot = '/img/app/create-invoice.jpg';
---
<Base
  title="Trucker Copilot for Owner Operators | Get Paid With Less Chasing"
  description="Submit trucking invoices, capture delivery documents, check funding status, and connect with transportation finance companies from one owner operator app."
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:2.5rem;">
    <div class="container hero__grid">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">For Owner Operators</span>
        <h1>You drive the truck. You should control the business.</h1>
        <p class="lead" style="color:var(--text-muted);">
          An owner operator cannot spend the day hauling freight and the night rebuilding paperwork.
          Trucker Copilot keeps the load, documents, funding status, and finance connection in one
          place so completed work can move forward.
        </p>
        <div class="hero__actions">
          <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="/download">Join as an Owner Operator</a>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="/funding-network">Find a Finance Company</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center;">
        <div class="phone-frame"><img src={shot} alt="Trucker Copilot owner operator dashboard" loading="eager" onerror="this.parentElement.classList.add('ph-fallback');this.remove()" /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero__grid mb-2">
        <div>
          <h2>Built around the pressure you actually carry</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.1rem;">
            Fuel, maintenance, insurance, payroll, and home expenses do not wait thirty, sixty, or
            ninety days. Trucker Copilot helps you submit completed loads quickly, follow the
            transaction, and connect with transportation finance providers when cash flow cannot
            wait on a broker payment cycle.
          </p>
        </div>
        <img class="photo" src="/img/photos/fuel-stop-driver.jpg" alt="Owner operator checking fuel prices on his phone at a truck stop" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--2 mt-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🚛</div>
          <h3>Submit from the cab</h3>
          <p>Capture the paperwork while the load is still fresh and send it without waiting to return to an office.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">👁️</div>
          <h3>See the status</h3>
          <p>Know whether the transaction is received, under review, missing information, approved, or funded when your provider supports the status.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>Check before accepting risk</h3>
          <p>Use available broker and shipper information to make a better decision before committing the truck.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Build your operating record</h3>
          <p>Verified activity and payment history can strengthen the story your business tells over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="Your truck moves the freight. Trucker Copilot moves the transaction."
    primaryLabel="Join as an Owner Operator"
    primaryHref="/download"
    secondaryLabel="Find a Finance Company"
    secondaryHref="/funding-network"
  />
</Base>
